  "description": "This individual is an undead human whose pale skinTone lies tightly over prominent bone, producing a drawn, cadaverous countenance. Gray eyes sit deep beneath heavy brow ridges, while black hair grows in sparse, uneven strands in an unkempt pattern that exposes a receded hairline. The jaw shows old, poorly set fractures that leave the mouth slightly skewed, and the hands present rigid, elongated fingers with darkened nailbeds typical of long decay. Their movement is governed by rote compulsion, and their presence is defined by silent, tireless persistence rather than breath or warmth.",
